summary:
Finally, a reference for the rival gang leader Raphael!
Bio: Leader of the Ricci Clan, Raphael is a cold, merciless force to be...
body:
Finally, a reference for the rival gang leader Raphael!

Bio: Leader of the Ricci Clan, Raphael is a cold, merciless force to be reckoned with. As the only qualified medic on his side of the Ruins, he can be a symbol of life or death to its inhabitants, charging outrageous amounts of money or favors for his services. Nicknamed the Grim Reaper, his weapon of choice is a scythe and is frequently seen with his pet crow, Tragedy (aka Bubo). He is in an on and off romantic relationship with Marshall, it being a rather toxic one mainly driven by lust. While he is power hungry, he is at a standstill against the Seraphim territory wise due to neither side wanting to relinquish their area.
